$interpreted: Royal Infantry: Give up! You'll never escape King Theodore!
Royal Infantry Captain: All your troops have been killed by our rune traps. There's no one to save you!
Angelia: All... killed?
Angelia: Colonel Levon, Sione...
Angelia: I should have been more careful... I shouldn't have fought against Theodore... their deaths are on my hands!
Lio: Angel, run!
Angelia: It's pointless. It's...
Lio: You can't give up! I've got your back, just like how Naya did back there!
Lio: ...R-Run, Angel. I'll hold them back!
Royal Infantry: Hah! what can some impure little demihuman do?
? ? ?: ...Then how about some pure bear muscle?
Dagger: Come on Princess, letting some poor kid give his life just so you can run away? You should be ashamed!
Angelia: Sir Dagger!? But... I heard you went missing!?
Dagger: You kidding me? You know how much trouble I've been through trying to find you!?
Angelia: You mean... you've been looking for me since the day I was kidnapped?
Dagger: That's right.
Dagger: Only until the whole continent was talking about how you made a castle fall from the sky did I find out that you were back in Totemtaff.
Angelia: That wasn't me!
Dagger: Whatever! Now that I've found you, I can finally say I'm a bear of my word!
Dagger: Now, anyone hungry for a claw sandwich?
Lio: Angel, let's go.
Dagger: Yeah, let's scram. What, your legs turn to jelly? How about a lift?
Angelia: I'll take you up on that. Let's get out of here.
Theodore: Not so fast!
